1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:21,000
 Evo ja sam Ivan Džanko,41 godina iz Osijeka, suprug žene Dajane koja je tu sa mnom,otac troje djece,Rafajla,Terezije i Rahele,osam godina,pet,godina i osam,devetnaest mjeseci i imamo jednu bebu na nebu.

2
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:29,000
 I evo prije nego što krenem sa svojim sredočanstvom, htio bih vas baš pidati kako ste.

3
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:40,000
 Jeste radosni?Jel uživate u sebi?Jel možete reći večera sad ovoga časa da uživate u svome životu, da uživate što postojite?

4
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:58,000
 Ko može, evo neka digne ruku u zrak.Evo,jedan dio da, drugi dio ne.Okej.Evo neka gospodin to večeras promjeni i neka gospodin radi ono što treba raditi, što će biti korisno za naše duše.

5
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:17,000
 Ali, evo, ja se usudim tako reći gospodinu.Ako bi ja smio nešto želiti gospodina ti večeras napraviš, onda je to da se večeras nanovo trajno obnove srca svih nas uspozna i da smo ludo ljubljeni.

6
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:35,300
 Ljubav, ljubav je ključ, sladunjava tema, to jaki duhovni mozgovi su več nadišli. Lako je vijek pričati o ljubavi, a treba raditi, treba biti odgovoran. Ali mi zaboravljamo da smo ljubljeni.

7
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:58,000
 Crkva slavi bezgrešno začeće, blažene djevice Marije. I možete zamisliti, sigurno ste čitili neke mističare, šta otac nebeski kaže o mami Mariji, kako ju gleda, kako ju ljubi, kako je bila radost i strast u našem nebeskom etati.

8
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:09,560
 Kad je zamislio, kad je odlučio, bit će moja Marija doće na ovaj svijet, donjeće moga sina, moja Marija, naša Marija.

9
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:12,460
 Možemo zamisliti koja je to strast u tati bila.

10
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:19,320
 A morate jednu stvar znat da bi ova duhovna obnova ili otvoreni susred, kako god hoćete, uspio.

11
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:23,120
 Morate znati jednu stvar, ali to je jako ozbiljno.

12
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:30,540
 Da to što ima mama Marija i kako ju tata gleda, to je nešto posebno.

13
00:02:30,540 --> 00:02:35,540
 Ali to što imaš ti, to nema mama Marija.

14
00:02:35,540 --> 00:02:39,640
 To nema mama Marija.

15
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:45,480
 To što imaš ti, to nema ni padre Pio, ni sveti Franjo.

16
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:47,660
 Taj original koji imaš ti.

17
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:53,380
 Taj original koji je u tebi kao trak zasedne tatine ljubavi.

18
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:55,580
 To nema nitko.

19
00:02:55,580 --> 00:03:01,280
 I to treba u tebi probuditi trajnju radost.

20
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:08,920
 Mi znamo kada neko umre svet, onda kaže, crkva kaže, rodio se za nebo.

21
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,340
 Rodio se za nebo.

22
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:13,260
 Kad umre na zemlji svet, čovjek je rodio se za nebo.

23
00:03:13,260 --> 00:03:16,240
 I u nebu je fešta i svi se rade.

24
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:19,740
 Zamislite kad je došao sveti Franjo primjeriti svoj nebo.

25
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:21,060
 Ko je morala biti fešta?

26
00:03:21,060 --> 00:03:22,360
 Njegov anđel, čuvar.

27
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,740
 Ko oranđela.

28
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:24,700
 Svi ga slave.

29
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:26,300
 Svi slave oca, boga.

30
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:27,700
 Evo, došao je.

31
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:29,520
 Došao je tvoj miljenik.

32
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:33,300
 Kog smo uživali gledati na zemlji, za kog smo uživali moliti.

33
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:35,240
 Za kog smo uživali navijati.

34
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,240
 Zdrži Franjo.

35
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:37,820
 Zdrži Franjo.

36
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:40,640
 Jer preko tebe je Bog na umio crku obnoviti.

37
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:43,260
 Sad zamislite da došao sveti Franjo fešta.

38
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:45,580
 Došao padre pio njegov sin.

39
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,140
 Grle se, fešta.

40
00:03:47,140 --> 00:03:49,980
 Došli drugi sveci fešta.

41
00:03:49,980 --> 00:03:52,040
 Trajna fešta, veselje.

42
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:54,860
 I dođeš ti onako...

43
00:03:54,860 --> 00:03:59,080
 Fešta je isto, ali onako kao...

44
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:01,460
 E, bravo, je, došao si i ti.

45
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:04,840
 Pa to bi bilo katastrofa nebo.

46
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,760
 A mi imamo taj stav puno puta.

47
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:11,180
 I dok sam se molio...

48
00:04:11,180 --> 00:04:12,980
 Kak to nakon je to, ovo je kliša onaj.

49
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:14,500
 Dok sam se molio za ovaj susret.

50
00:04:18,080 --> 00:04:20,180
 Čuo sam jedno pitanje u sebi.

51
00:04:20,180 --> 00:04:24,360
 Koje je, mislim, na početku Miša izgovorio.

52
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:28,640
 On je u molitvi govorio o pripremi za ovaj susret.

53
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,760
 Pa sam čuo jedno pitanje.

54
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:33,580
 Šta očekuješ od ovog susrta?

55
00:04:33,580 --> 00:04:35,320
 Jesi li pitao Isusa?

56
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:39,760
 Jesi li došao, išao prema ovom susretu sa isčekivanjem

57
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,260
 i traženjem od gospodina?

58
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:42,780
 Što želiš od njega?

59
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:45,100
 Možda samo je, želim te srest.

60
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:47,300
 Želim večeras biti sa tobom.

61
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:53,320
 Ili si došao iz navike, jer se podrazumijeva da je ovdje sila gospodnja?

62
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,160
 I je.

63
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:57,660
 Jer se i podrazumijeva da će ovdje Bog djelovati?

64
00:04:57,660 --> 00:04:58,880
 I hoće.

65
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,740
 Ali će zaobić tebe?

66
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:07,140
 Ako nemaš čežnju i ako nisi došao sa tim isčekivanjem

67
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:11,740
 bez ovog lošeg podrazumijevanja, loše strane podrazumijevanja,

68
00:05:11,740 --> 00:05:15,580
 a to je da Bog će biti, radi će, dolazi će, spoznaje,

69
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:20,320
 bit će jako slavlje, bit će jaki nagovori, ali tebe će zaobić.

70
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:27,540
 Ako, ako barem sada, jer sad imaš priliku da zapravo te ne zaobiće,

71
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:30,200
 kažeš, gospodine, želim te sresti.

72
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:32,640
 Želim večeras biti sa tobom.

73
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:33,920
 Jer to je ključ.

74
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:42,220
 Gledajte, ja kao otac troje djece, prema svakom djetetu imam svoj odnos poseban

75
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:49,080
 i ja bi bio loš tata, vjerujte mi, loš tata po zakonu ljubavi,

76
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:54,600
 kada ne bih svaki dan, kada dolazim, kad se budim ili idem na posao,

77
00:05:54,600 --> 00:06:00,840
 dolazim svoje kući, kad ne bih imao čežnju pokazat svakom od svoje djece

78
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,060
 da ih posebno ljubim.

79
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:05,740
 Ja bi bio loš tata, zakinio bi njih u ljubavi.

80
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:13,500
 I ja kada dolazem kuć s posla, onda kako za svako djete imam neku posebnu foru,

81
00:06:13,500 --> 00:06:19,380
 zezanciju, nekome fičukam od djece, onda melodiju koji samo to djete zna,

82
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:21,060
 to je znak, tata je došao.

83
00:06:21,060 --> 00:06:25,640
 A nekome otpijam neku pjesmicu, to drugo djete zna, to je moja pjesmica,

84
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:26,480
 tata je došao.

85
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:29,500
 Znate što bude, ali svaki dan, evo moja žena je svjedok,

86
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:37,620
 svaki dan, kad lozim u kuću, tatice, a ja većem ljubljeni, svaki dan.

87
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:40,960
 I tu nema umaranja, tu nema umaranja.

88
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:48,140
 Moramo biti strogi prema djeci, odgovorni, ljubav, tako ta malostadunjava,

89
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:53,920
 to zna ono, ovoga, djecu možda ne pomagati im da se gibaju odgovornosti,

90
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:59,980
 ne, ljubav je odgovorn, ljubav ne može dopustiti da djete nazaduje,

91
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:05,900
 i ljubav imaju određenu i pedagogiju i strogoću, ako hoćete, pravedno, sve, sve, da, da, da,

92
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:09,160
 ali uvijek mora biti osjećaj ljubavi.

93
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:14,400
 Moja djeca moraju zna da su ljubljena, moraju zna da su ljubljena.

94
00:07:14,540 --> 00:07:17,840
 Ja, ja grešan, Ivan, se u tome ne naprežem.

95
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,620
 Pazite, ovo, to je milost.

96
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:22,980
 Ja se ne naprežem, grešan čovjek.

97
00:07:22,980 --> 00:07:25,240
 A zamislite nebeski otac.

98
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:29,160
 I evo još, prije nego što krene ovoga sredočanstvo,

99
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,280
 još jedna stvar.

100
00:07:33,780 --> 00:07:36,240
 Mi smo krenuli slaviti, baš je bilo divno.

101
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,180
 Stvarno se to lijepo pomazanje osjeti,

102
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:41,020
 vidi se da je ovdje duh sveti na dijelu,

103
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:44,500
 da je zdrava zajednica, zdravo zajedništvo.

104
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:47,660
 I ne znam jeste li razmišljali,

105
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:50,720
 odakle je slavlje nama.

106
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,440
 Slavljenički nas je preljepo izanimirao,

107
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,660
 pomagao nam.

108
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:57,580
 Ali znate gdje, odakle slavlje u nama.

109
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:59,620
 Pjesme mogu biti ovake, onake

110
00:07:59,620 --> 00:08:03,040
 i mogu biti malo jači, malo slabiji,

111
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,340
 umorni, opterećeni, manji opterećeni.

112
00:08:05,340 --> 00:08:07,680
 To sve isto ima neku malu ulogu,

113
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,500
 ali veselje, radost dolazi,

114
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:12,640
 jer je ovdje Bog prisutan.

115
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:16,160
 I Bog je prisutan, kako je prisutan?

116
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:20,060
 Sa srcem koje je došlo sa očekivanjem.

117
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:22,160
 Isus je ovdje sa očekivanjem.

118
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:26,640
 On je došao, ne kao visoko crkveni dostanek,

119
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,680
 evo, došao je na jedan skup crkveni.

120
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:31,540
 I došao je, tu je, po defoltu.

121
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:34,400
 On mora biti tu, to je njegovo mjesto.

122
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:37,920
 Ne, on je došao sa radošću.

123
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:40,640
 I mi smo na trenutak osjetili,

124
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,840
 samo na trenutak,

125
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,880
 ili malo mi osjećamo,

126
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:47,100
 jer na zemlji ne možemo nikad osjetiti

127
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,340
 kao na nebu punini,

128
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:51,620
 mi malo osjetimo radost njegovu,

129
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:53,400
 pa ta radost prelazi na nas.

130
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,420
 Kao kad ste u prisutnosti zla,

131
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:57,220
 osjetite da nešto ne valja

132
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:59,320
 i kažete, ja imam neku nelagudu,

133
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,820
 osjećam nešto u prostoriji,

134
00:09:00,820 --> 00:09:02,180
 je baš onako teško.

135
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:04,880
 Nešto je što ne valja tu.

136
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:07,140
 Ali ovdje je Bog koji se raduje.

137
00:09:08,180 --> 00:09:11,760
 Evo, to je ključ da sve drugo možemo čuti

138
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:15,140
 i primiti odanas do zauvijek,

139
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:18,700
 dok te god budete dolazili na novorođene,

140
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:22,960
 dok te god budete dolazili sve ove godine,

141
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:27,540
 ključ će biti upravo ovo da svatko od vas zna

142
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:29,040
 ja sam taj original.

143
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:29,780
 Sam zamislite,

144
00:09:29,780 --> 00:09:33,580
 zamislite koliko će Miša morat manje vas animirat,

145
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:36,380
 koliko će morat manje,

146
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:38,400
 pardon, ispričavam se,

147
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:41,360
 koliko će morati manje vas animirati

148
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:44,320
 kada vi budete svi znali

149
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,520
 i to prenosili drugima

150
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,920
 ja sam original.

151
00:09:46,920 --> 00:09:48,800
 Nitko nije kao ja.

152
00:09:48,800 --> 00:09:51,680
 I onda tek kad to shvatiš,

153
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:54,540
 onda se okreneš desno i ljevo

154
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:57,500
 i vidiš, wow, čovječe,

155
00:09:57,500 --> 00:10:01,460
 kaka divota, kako poštovanje,

156
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:02,940
 nema svađa,

157
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:04,940
 pa vidi ovog originala,

158
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,040
 nitko nije kao on,

159
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,660
 nitko nije kao on.

160
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,540
 I tu se događa proboj.

161
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:11,280
 I to Bog želi.

162
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,040
 Evo, Bog,

163
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:15,000
 ustavim se reći da može biti tužan

164
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,400
 ako ti to ne znaš.

165
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,640
 Ako se ti ne radoješ sebi

166
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,820
 kao što se crkva radoje danas

167
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:23,120
 bezgrešnom začeću,

168
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,200
 Mame Marije.

169
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:26,680
 Evo,

170
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:29,360
 moj život ide ovako.

171
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:32,220
 Rođen sam kao vrlo mlad.

172
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:35,880
 82. godine,

173
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:38,300
 1. travnja, 1. aprila.

174
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,740
 Gospodin se našal je malo sa mnom

175
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,880
 i sa mojim roditeljima.

176
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,540
 I evo,

177
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:48,060
 od malena sam bio Kristov,

178
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:51,440
 ali nisam uvijek bio sa Kristom.

179
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:53,220
 Imam još brata,

180
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:55,120
 starijega, 4 godine od sebe.

181
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:55,740
 I evo,

182
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:57,320
 klasika,

183
00:10:57,320 --> 00:11:01,000
 iz tradicionalne sam katoličke obitelji,

184
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,800
 primio sve sakramente,

185
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:06,620
 zahvalan roditeljima što su me krstili u vjeri

186
00:11:06,620 --> 00:11:08,580
 i što su mi dali,

187
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:09,660
 to što su mi dali,

188
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:11,200
 no onaj dio

189
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,060
 koji je nedostajao,

190
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:14,760
 koji je kasnije pomješan

191
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,740
 sa mojim osobnim grijesima

192
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:17,880
 i lošim odlukama,

193
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,780
 mene je odveo na krivi put

194
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,580
 i bio taj da je falilo,

195
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:21,860
 evo,

196
00:11:21,860 --> 00:11:25,180
 onako kad sam gledao malo u prošlost,

197
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,040
 u svoju obitelj,

198
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,900
 falilo je te kulture,

199
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:29,720
 ako hoćete,

200
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,940
 razgovora o Isusu,

201
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:32,980
 falilo je osobne molitve,

202
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,520
 falilo je predanja Isusu,

203
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,760
 falilo je ove priče,

204
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:36,980
 ove jasnoće,

205
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,060
 da smo originali,

206
00:11:38,060 --> 00:11:40,620
 da nitko nije kao ti

207
00:11:40,620 --> 00:11:44,000
 i da se u tom duhu trebamo razvijati,

208
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,380
 a sve drugo,

209
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,640
 kako nam sam Isus kaže,

210
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,560
 bit će nadodano.

211
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,420
 I evo,

212
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:51,580
 kao i u svakoj obitelji,

213
00:11:51,580 --> 00:11:54,640
 kada nema prisutnog duha gospodnjega

214
00:11:54,640 --> 00:11:55,980
 u punini,

215
00:11:55,980 --> 00:11:57,520
 kako jedan obitelj treba imati,

216
00:11:57,520 --> 00:11:59,800
 onda pušu drugi duhovi,

217
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:04,660
 pušu sve požude ovoga svijeta,

218
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:05,300
 ponude.

219
00:12:05,300 --> 00:12:07,960
 I tako sam i ja,

220
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,640
 evo, nekako u jednom trenutku

221
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,240
 svoga života izgubio se,

222
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:14,700
 negdje sam bio izgubljen

223
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,320
 upravo u tom identitetu,

224
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,140
 tko sam,

225
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:19,300
 što sam i što radim,

226
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:22,240
 na ovome svijetu.

227
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:22,920
 Ali,

228
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:25,840
 gospodin je od uvijek bio sa mnom,

229
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,500
 od malena.

230
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:27,140
 I,

231
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:29,860
 dao mi jedne posebne milosti,

232
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:31,720
 ja ću malo danas govoriti večeras

233
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,020
 o nekim nadnaravnim zapatima,

234
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:36,340
 gospodin koji mi je gospodin dopustio,

235
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:37,140
 da me učvrsti,

236
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:37,780
 uspoznaje,

237
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:39,720
 da sam njegov miljenik,

238
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:41,400
 ali da to onda mogu kasnije

239
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,500
 nesebično dijeliti drugima

240
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,840
 i pomaga drugima da shvate

241
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:48,140
 da su miljenici i originali.

242
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:50,920
 Gospodin mi je puno puta dolazio

243
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,140
 u snovima.

244
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:53,140
 Kao mali,

245
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:55,440
 znao sam ga sanjati,

246
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:57,100
 i to znao sam ga sanjati

247
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:58,720
 u kući moje pokojne bake,

248
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,920
 tamo se odvijao san,

249
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:02,780
 ja sam zapravo bio u svom stanu,

250
00:13:02,780 --> 00:13:04,200
 u roditeljskom stanu,

251
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:06,680
 ali kad sam sanjio Isusa,

252
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:08,400
 uvijek je događaj bio

253
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,840
 da smo bili u kući moje pokojne bake,

254
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:13,120
 u kojoj sam kasnije živio

255
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,380
 i gdje sam doživio

256
00:13:14,380 --> 00:13:17,140
 duboki zahvat Božje ljubav

257
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:18,800
 i jedno ono duboko obraćenje.

258
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:22,260
 Puno mi je gospodin davao snova,

259
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:23,860
 dakle sanjam njega,

260
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:25,400
 uzmem me u naručje

261
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:26,820
 ili sanjam oca,

262
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:29,900
 imam jasnoću da me otac nebeske drži,

263
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,540
 stavi me u krilo

264
00:13:31,540 --> 00:13:32,960
 i govore mi,

265
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,500
 ali ja ništa ne mogu čuti,

266
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,600
 ali mi govore.

267
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:38,400
 I znam da sam siguran, miran,

268
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:40,740
 ali nije mi dano bilo da čujem.

269
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,740
 Kad god bi se ja probudio,

270
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:46,360
 uvijek bi to rekao svoje mami.

271
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,920
 Šta god mi se duhovno u životu događalo,

272
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:50,900
 uvijek bi imao svjedoka,

273
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,560
 nekako me tako gospodin vodio,

274
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:55,080
 samo iz mene to izlazilo,

275
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:56,660
 šta god da doživim,

276
00:13:56,660 --> 00:13:58,520
 dobijem neki navješte nečega,

277
00:13:58,520 --> 00:14:00,340
 dobijem neku jasnoću

278
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:01,500
 ili neku sliku,

279
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:03,300
 kako mi to kažemo,

280
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,060
 proročku sliku,

281
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:05,460
 sliku, proročku riječ,

282
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:06,800
 ja bih to odmah podijelio.

283
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,100
 Ona bih to rekao mami,

284
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:08,740
 ili kasnije

285
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:11,740
 nekome od duhovnih ljudi,

286
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,440
 tako da sljedećavanstvo bude

287
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,860
 jako jasno

288
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:16,300
 i da znamo da je to bio gospodin

289
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:17,240
 kad se stvari dogode.

290
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,560
 I evo i tako,

291
00:14:18,560 --> 00:14:19,620
 osim tih snova

292
00:14:19,620 --> 00:14:21,720
 gdje me gospodin držaj govorio,

293
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:23,840
 recimo imao sam jedan zanimljiv san

294
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:28,300
 u 1990. godine,

295
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:30,060
 sanjao sam

296
00:14:30,060 --> 00:14:33,220
 šahovsku ploču

297
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:35,680
 i kako imate crne i bijele figure

298
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,680
 i dvije ruke povlače poteze.

299
00:14:37,680 --> 00:14:40,600
 I kako jedna ruka povuče potez,

300
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:42,600
 imao sam jasnoću da se radi o

301
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,740
 muslimanima i kršćanima.

302
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:47,180
 jedna ruka povuče potez,

303
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:48,720
 kada ona povuče potez,

304
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:49,760
 ja sam vidio avione

305
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,380
 kako se dižu

306
00:14:51,380 --> 00:14:53,040
 i idu napast

307
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:55,580
 muslimansku zemlju Irak

308
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:57,140
 i bombardiraju ju.

309
00:14:57,140 --> 00:14:59,420
 I ja sam se probudio,

310
00:14:59,420 --> 00:15:00,760
 pazite to je doba,

311
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,640
 bez interneta,

312
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:04,140
 bez brzine vijesti.

313
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:06,960
 I ja kažem mami šta sam sanjao,

314
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:07,580
 ja kažem mama,

315
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:09,320
 vidio sam veliki rat

316
00:15:09,320 --> 00:15:11,340
 i baš je bilo strašno,

317
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:12,560
 uplašio sam se.

318
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:15,300
 I prošlo je možda,

319
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,780
 koji mjesec,

320
00:15:16,780 --> 00:15:17,840
 mjesec dva,

321
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:20,360
 jedno jutro smo se probudili,

322
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:22,200
 ono, TV je uvijek gvorio,

323
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,740
 upaljene neke vijesti,

324
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:26,020
 kaže u ranim jutarnim satima,

325
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:29,680
 Amerikanci su digli avione

326
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:32,000
 i bombardirali Irak,

327
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,440
 koji je tamo jedan Kuwait bio,

328
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:34,740
 zapasio.

329
00:15:34,740 --> 00:15:39,560
 Nakon domovinskog rata,

330
00:15:39,560 --> 00:15:41,280
 kad je bila mirna reintegracija

331
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:42,280
 naše Slavonije,

332
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:45,380
 sanjao sam veliku poplavu,

333
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:48,620
 i u mjestu Aljmaš

334
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:50,660
 i u snu sam vidio

335
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:52,940
 kako je cijelo nogometno igralište

336
00:15:52,940 --> 00:15:53,740
 poplavljeno

337
00:15:53,740 --> 00:15:55,140
 i samo stativa viri

338
00:15:55,140 --> 00:15:56,200
 iznad vode.

339
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:58,060
 Ja mami kažem,

340
00:15:58,060 --> 00:15:59,520
 to je tako stvaran san,

341
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:00,540
 kao da sam tamo

342
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,800
 i opet je kažem,

343
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,220
 čuju sam,

344
00:16:02,220 --> 00:16:03,540
 ja sam baš u poplavu

345
00:16:03,540 --> 00:16:04,340
 u Aljmaš

346
00:16:04,340 --> 00:16:05,360
 i sve to joj opišem.

347
00:16:06,620 --> 00:16:07,500
 Nismo mi tad znali,

348
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,320
 ni mama, ni ja,

349
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:10,360
 da postoji zagovorna molitva.

350
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,560
 Znate, zagovorna molitva

351
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:12,500
 nije od neki dan

352
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,160
 iz karizmatskih krugova,

353
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,100
 nego i od uvijek,

354
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:15,880
 ali evo,

355
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:17,000
 hvala dragom Bogu,

356
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:17,860
 u ovo novo je vrijeme,

357
00:16:17,860 --> 00:16:19,440
 gospodina suči,

358
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,380
 daje nam povuku

359
00:16:20,380 --> 00:16:21,840
 i onda imamo to lijepo organizirano

360
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,780
 i jasno zašto je potrebno

361
00:16:24,780 --> 00:16:26,680
 biti dio zagovorne molitve

362
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:27,780
 za sve Bože stvari.

363
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:29,080
 Pa ono,

364
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,640
 ja sam to samo primio

365
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:31,220
 i rekao,

366
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:33,280
 kad jedan dan isto,

367
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:36,760
 dosta se u biti prije

368
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:38,140
 okupljalo oko televizora.

369
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:39,120
 Mi djeca,

370
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:42,320
 gledali smo centralni dnevnik,

371
00:16:42,320 --> 00:16:43,960
 to je bilo prije toga

372
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:44,840
 Crtić dnevnik

373
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:46,440
 i tako malo ozbiljnjena

374
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,160
 smo bili djeca.

375
00:16:47,160 --> 00:16:50,220
 I gledamo mi dnevnik

376
00:16:50,220 --> 00:16:52,360
 reportaža iz Aljmaša,

377
00:16:52,360 --> 00:16:54,180
 poplava u Slavoniji,

378
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,560
 mirana integracija kaže,

379
00:16:56,560 --> 00:16:57,780
 može se ući tamo,

380
00:16:57,780 --> 00:17:01,020
 HRT stavlja sliku iz Aljmaša,

381
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:02,440
 poplava,

382
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:03,700
 poplavljeno igralište

383
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:04,840
 i snimaju stativu

384
00:17:04,840 --> 00:17:05,880
 kako viri iznad.

385
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,480
 I mama i ja se gledamo,

386
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,640
 ne možemo da od sebi.

387
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,580
 Pa čovječ,

388
00:17:09,580 --> 00:17:10,420
 ovo sam sanja,

389
00:17:10,420 --> 00:17:11,160
 ovo sam vidio.

390
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:13,140
 I evo,

391
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:15,280
 tako puno puta mi gospodin

392
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,660
 kroz nove progovarao

393
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:18,140
 i onda ima jedan san

394
00:17:18,140 --> 00:17:19,620
 koji je obilježio

395
00:17:19,620 --> 00:17:20,680
 moj život.

396
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,200
 Sad sam u dobi

397
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:25,180
 kada sam zalutao,

398
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:26,980
 tinejđer sam,

399
00:17:26,980 --> 00:17:28,840
 izgubio sam se,

400
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:31,760
 počeo sam čeznat

401
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:33,460
 za svetom ljubavlju,

402
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:35,560
 nisam znao da sam ljubljen.

403
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:37,940
 Dobio sam ljubavi od oca do majke,

404
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,500
 svako mi je dao koliko je mogo,

405
00:17:39,500 --> 00:17:40,500
 koliko je znao,

406
00:17:41,180 --> 00:17:42,900
 ali nema one jasnoće

407
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:44,060
 da sam orginal.

408
00:17:44,060 --> 00:17:46,220
 I otiša sam,

409
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:47,460
 kao i mnogi mladi,

410
00:17:47,460 --> 00:17:49,660
 u ono što svijet nudi,

411
00:17:49,660 --> 00:17:51,640
 one privremene užitke

412
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:52,540
 koje nadomjestaju

413
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:53,480
 pravo ljubav,

414
00:17:53,480 --> 00:17:54,600
 bludnost,

415
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:56,040
 izlazci,

416
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:58,320
 smiješne cigarete

417
00:17:58,320 --> 00:18:00,920
 i take gluposti,

418
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:01,940
 take sve stvari,

419
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:02,200
 jel?

420
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,900
 I

421
00:18:03,900 --> 00:18:05,500
 totalno sam se izgubio.

422
00:18:05,500 --> 00:18:07,260
 Došao sam do toga,

423
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:09,500
 ove sad popratne okolnosti

424
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,380
 su grozne

425
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:11,500
 i one zarobljavaju

426
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,560
 i one su opasne,

427
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:14,640
 ali ono što sam ja vidio,

428
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,480
 što je bilo još opasnije

429
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,160
 u meni,

430
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,260
 je što sam ja izgubio

431
00:18:18,260 --> 00:18:19,220
 volju za životom.

432
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:20,940
 To je najveća,

433
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:21,360
 zapravo,

434
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,600
 pobjeda zloga

435
00:18:22,600 --> 00:18:23,740
 nad nekim čovjekom,

436
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:25,060
 da ti izgubiš

437
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,380
 volju za životom.

438
00:18:26,880 --> 00:18:28,080
 radosti da ne pričam,

439
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:29,200
 nema radosti nigdje.

440
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:30,500
 Želim umrijeti,

441
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:31,040
 a mlad sam.

442
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:32,280
 Poraz.

443
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:34,880
 I zavapio sam negdje

444
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,800
 onako u sebi,

445
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,180
 ni sam,

446
00:18:36,180 --> 00:18:36,860
 ne znam kako,

447
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:38,240
 točno ni kojim riječima,

448
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:40,180
 barim da se nešto promijeni.

449
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,280
 A pratio me je snažni

450
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:43,880
 osjećaj krivnje,

451
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:46,300
 vidim godine su neke prošle,

452
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:48,100
 nakon da bi još jasnoću,

453
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:49,420
 nema povratka,

454
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:50,860
 čovječe,

455
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:51,780
 šta sada je?

456
00:18:51,780 --> 00:18:52,880
 Kako tužno.

457
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:55,120
 I samo da se nešto promijeni.

458
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:56,340
 I sanjam san.

459
00:18:56,880 --> 00:18:59,160
 sanjam san

460
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,820
 u mojej zgradi

461
00:19:00,820 --> 00:19:01,780
 gdje sam živio,

462
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:04,080
 u hodniku,

463
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:05,120
 onak malo čudan san,

464
00:19:05,120 --> 00:19:08,420
 gospina slika.

465
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:12,460
 iz slike izlazi

466
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:13,860
 nakon glava gospina

467
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,240
 i ruka

468
00:19:15,240 --> 00:19:18,000
 i ovako ruka mi pokazuje,

469
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,580
 samo ovako mi pokaže.

470
00:19:20,580 --> 00:19:23,160
 Pogled

471
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,740
 gospe te žene

472
00:19:24,740 --> 00:19:25,620
 u tom trenutku,

473
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:28,560
 nisam još njimao skroz jasnoće,

474
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:30,720
 da je to gospa,

475
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:31,840
 kroz koji dan mi ono tek

476
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:32,860
 onako psinulo.

477
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:35,340
 Bio je strog,

478
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:37,260
 majčinski,

479
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:38,240
 majčinski strog,

480
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,240
 nisam imao nemir,

481
00:19:39,440 --> 00:19:40,840
 i tu sam znao

482
00:19:40,840 --> 00:19:42,820
 da je to Božja stvar,

483
00:19:42,820 --> 00:19:44,120
 nego ono,

484
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:44,460
 gledaj,

485
00:19:44,460 --> 00:19:45,820
 krajnje vrijeme,

486
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:48,540
 ako ti se život ne okrene

487
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:49,800
 skroz na dobro,

488
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:52,000
 neće bi dobro za tebe.

489
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,720
 I jasnoća,

490
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,240
 ona ništa mi nije rekla,

491
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,020
 ali jasnoća,

492
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:57,180
 kako mi ona progovara

493
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:58,380
 i kaže

494
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,680
 otiđi u Međugorje.

495
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:02,760
 Ja sam mlad,

496
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:03,800
 nema nikakve

497
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:04,580
 tu sad

498
00:20:04,580 --> 00:20:05,700
 onake zajednice,

499
00:20:05,700 --> 00:20:07,260
 nekih puteva u Međugorje,

500
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:08,720
 ništa.

501
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,100
 Rekao, ok,

502
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:11,420
 moram ići u Međugorje,

503
00:20:11,420 --> 00:20:12,040
 to je to ono,

504
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:12,640
 jasno mi je.

505
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:15,360
 Uzimam glas Slavonije,

506
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:16,640
 lokalne novine,

507
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,840
 koje su nama bila

508
00:20:18,840 --> 00:20:20,560
 zezancija u gradu Osijeku,

509
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:21,600
 da ono što piše

510
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:24,380
 u večernjem danas,

511
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:26,600
 to će sutra pisati

512
00:20:26,600 --> 00:20:27,520
 u glasu Slavonije.

513
00:20:27,520 --> 00:20:29,120
 Da mi izvine

514
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:30,760
 svi iz glasa Slavonija

515
00:20:30,760 --> 00:20:31,660
 koji ko bude gledao,

516
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:33,200
 to je bila jedna šala,

517
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,360
 jer mi nismo znali

518
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,180
 cijeni dovoljno

519
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:36,820
 sve što rade,

520
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:37,260
 novine.

521
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:40,660
 I uzem ja glas Slavonije

522
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:41,480
 netipično,

523
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:43,920
 čito sam večernji jučer

524
00:20:43,920 --> 00:20:46,100
 i okrenem,

525
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:48,160
 kad oglas

526
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:50,540
 hodočašće u Međugorje,

527
00:20:50,540 --> 00:20:52,060
 da će ono,

528
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,320
 ovo nema smisla,

529
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,620
 čoveč u glasu Slavonije,

530
00:20:54,620 --> 00:20:55,340
 taki oglas,

531
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:56,360
 slavno netipično,

532
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:56,640
 ništa,

533
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:57,840
 ja okrenem telefon

534
00:20:57,840 --> 00:20:59,780
 ovoga

535
00:20:59,780 --> 00:21:01,220
 i prijavim se.

536
00:21:01,220 --> 00:21:02,400
 Sjedem u neki bus,

537
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:02,840
 bake,

538
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,400
 djedovi,

539
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,180
 neki tamo ljudi

540
00:21:04,180 --> 00:21:05,040
 nešto animiraju,

541
00:21:05,040 --> 00:21:05,760
 pričaju,

542
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:07,800
 učučurio se tamo,

543
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:08,660
 sam da stignem

544
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:09,460
 i ne znam da idem

545
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:10,800
 i ništa,

546
00:21:10,800 --> 00:21:12,120
 stigo ja u Međugorje

547
00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:15,460
 i tamo doživim

548
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:16,780
 milost na milost.

549
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:19,660
 prvi put sam bio na klanjanju,

550
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:21,860
 znate koji ste svi bili u Međugorje,

551
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:22,380
 vjerojatno,

552
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:24,540
 ono vanjski oltar,

553
00:21:24,540 --> 00:21:26,960
 lijepo proljetno doljetno vrijeme,

554
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:29,080
 ja sam na koljenima,

555
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:30,560
 pred presvetim

556
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:33,800
 i događa se eksplozija ljubavi.

557
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:37,340
 Dobivam jasnoću

558
00:21:37,340 --> 00:21:39,860
 u svome srcu

559
00:21:39,860 --> 00:21:40,980
 da je Bog živ.

560
00:21:40,980 --> 00:21:43,840
 I to na jedan čudesan način,

561
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,760
 na jedan čudesan način,

562
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:47,840
 počinjem čut u sebi

563
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:51,420
 glas

564
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:52,900
 kroz moje misli

565
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:53,800
 da ne bude ništa

566
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:54,880
 sa spektakularno,

567
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,280
 ništa mistično,

568
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:58,820
 nisam nikakvi fizički glas čuo,

569
00:21:58,820 --> 00:22:00,580
 nego glas u svome srcu,

570
00:22:00,580 --> 00:22:03,640
 imate ta iskustva sigurno,

571
00:22:03,640 --> 00:22:05,520
 koji paralelno

572
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:06,200
 mi govori,

573
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,120
 dok mi neko drugi nešto priča,

574
00:22:08,120 --> 00:22:09,940
 mogu slušati jedno i drugo.

575
00:22:09,940 --> 00:22:11,840
 Umirujući jasan glas

576
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:13,540
 da mi se javlja nebeski tata.

577
00:22:13,540 --> 00:22:15,260
 Kao mali,

578
00:22:15,260 --> 00:22:17,040
 ja sam imao relaciju sa Bogom,

579
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:17,920
 kako sam vam rekao,

580
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:19,720
 ali ta relacija bila Isus Krist.

581
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:21,640
 Mama Marija,

582
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:23,740
 tu i tamo nekad je se spomeneš,

583
00:22:23,740 --> 00:22:25,740
 ali Isus Krist je bio centralna ličnost.

584
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:27,380
 Međutim, ovdje

585
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:29,540
 čujem u sebi

586
00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:31,620
 glas nebeskoga oca,

587
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:33,340
 koji mi govori da je moj tata,

588
00:22:33,340 --> 00:22:35,000
 da je,

589
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:37,860
 čuo moju patnju,

590
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:39,980
 da je vidio moju bol,

591
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:43,060
 da je vidio da nema nikog da mi dođe,

592
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:44,440
 da mi pomogne

593
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:45,380
 i kaže,

594
00:22:45,380 --> 00:22:47,980
 ja sam odlučio da ti se javim.

595
00:22:48,620 --> 00:22:51,380
 odlučio sam da te dovedem u mir,

596
00:22:51,380 --> 00:22:52,300
 u svoju ljubav.

597
00:22:53,560 --> 00:22:55,100
 ja slušam te stvari,

598
00:22:55,100 --> 00:22:57,160
 plaćem, plaćem,

599
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:58,620
 na koljenima,

600
00:22:58,620 --> 00:23:00,560
 sad, vremena, ridam,

601
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:02,040
 završava klanjanje,

602
00:23:02,040 --> 00:23:04,120
 ljudi se dižu,

603
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:05,320
 idu u svoje pansione,

604
00:23:05,320 --> 00:23:06,720
 ja klećim i plaćam.

605
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,240
 ne mogu se smiriti,

606
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,220
 ljudi me tupkaju,

607
00:23:10,220 --> 00:23:12,460
 po ramenu maze me,

608
00:23:12,460 --> 00:23:14,260
 imaju potprevu,

609
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,620
 red sve će biti dobro.

610
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:18,020
 Vjerojatno su neki karizmatici

611
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:19,080
 imali spozir,

612
00:23:19,080 --> 00:23:19,820
 da treba moliti,

613
00:23:19,820 --> 00:23:22,260
 znate kako ima ruke lete.

614
00:23:22,260 --> 00:23:25,820
 Ali ja ništa nisam doživljavo,

615
00:23:25,820 --> 00:23:26,680
 samo ono,

616
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:27,600
 ma to je to,

617
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,540
 hvala s vima,

618
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:30,240
 ne znam ni šta se događa okolo,

619
00:23:30,240 --> 00:23:32,020
 ali i ovo što se unutra događa

620
00:23:32,020 --> 00:23:33,260
 je čudesno.

621
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:37,420
 I dolazim na sljedeće klanjanje,

622
00:23:37,420 --> 00:23:39,520
 tako dolazim iz godina u godinu,

623
00:23:39,520 --> 00:23:40,120
 u Međugorje,

624
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:41,720
 i tamo,

625
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,000
 šta se događa?

626
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:45,600
 Otac Nebeski u Međugorju,

627
00:23:45,700 --> 00:23:47,320
 kad sam se vratio u Osijek,

628
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:48,660
 neprestano mi je progovarao,

629
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:50,360
 šeto sam po ulicama grada,

630
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:54,960
 Osijek je negdje sto tisuća stanovnika,

631
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,500
 možda malčice i manje,

632
00:23:56,500 --> 00:24:00,600
 i to je onako mal grad,

633
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:03,360
 ja sam se malo nešto bavio malim nogometom,

634
00:24:03,360 --> 00:24:04,740
 znaš svoju generaciju,

635
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:06,040
 ja vam mošćaj sam i u Osijeku,

636
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,620
 svi znamo,

637
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:07,160
 evo iskreno,

638
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:09,020
 nije sad mal mal,

639
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:11,420
 ali nešto nije ni specialno veli grad za mene.

640
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:14,140
 I vraćam se tamo,

641
00:24:14,140 --> 00:24:15,320
 znam da me ljudi znaju,

642
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:16,700
 znaju me i sa gluposti,

643
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:19,980
 jer nekad sam imao potrebu se dokazivati,

644
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:22,340
 kad sam to otišao u loše stvari,

645
00:24:22,340 --> 00:24:25,620
 da bih skrenio pažnju na sebe,

646
00:24:25,620 --> 00:24:26,200
 da sam živ,

647
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:28,340
 da postajem i da trebam ljubav.

648
00:24:29,520 --> 00:24:34,160
 I sad hodam tamo promenadom našom osječkom šetalištem uz rijeku Dravu,

649
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,720
 plaćem,

650
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:38,120
 dignem ruke u zrak,

651
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:40,240
 zahvaljujem Bogu,

652
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:44,680
 puca glas kod nekih ljudi koji me znaju da je džanko puko,

653
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:48,100
 ali meni to ništa nije bilo.

654
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:48,960
 Gledam njih,

655
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:50,200
 gledam po kafićima,

656
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,320
 puni kafići,

657
00:24:51,320 --> 00:24:54,140
 ta promenada naša imala je kafić za kafića,

658
00:24:54,140 --> 00:24:56,140
 puno sve,

659
00:24:56,140 --> 00:24:57,300
 proljeće ljeto,

660
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,240
 svi prpošni.

661
00:24:58,240 --> 00:24:59,820
 Ja plaćem,

662
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:00,820
 molim za njih,

663
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:01,360
 gledam,

664
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:03,920
 kad bi oni znali koliko ih Bog ljubi,

665
00:25:03,920 --> 00:25:05,760
 luda situacija,

666
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:07,740
 ali u meni živa

667
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:09,340
 i nemam skrupula,

668
00:25:09,340 --> 00:25:10,320
 nemam srama,

669
00:25:10,320 --> 00:25:11,700
 hodam takav.

670
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:14,080
 I tata mi govori,

671
00:25:14,080 --> 00:25:15,680
 govorim i govorim.

672
00:25:15,680 --> 00:25:18,060
 I pošalje me opet u Međugorje.

673
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:19,040
 Odem u Međugorje,

674
00:25:19,040 --> 00:25:20,100
 opet klanjanje

675
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:21,640
 i onda mi otac kaže,

676
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:25,040
 sad ću te učiti

677
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:26,640
 nutarnjem glasu.

678
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:30,140
 Učit ću te da slušaš moje riječi

679
00:25:30,140 --> 00:25:32,040
 i da mi vjeruješ.

680
00:25:32,040 --> 00:25:34,060
 To je jako bitno za tvoj život.

681
00:25:35,140 --> 00:25:37,460
 i znate kako on u Međugorje,

682
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,300
 o tata su mi klanjanje

683
00:25:38,300 --> 00:25:39,260
 uvijek bila najljepša.

684
00:25:39,260 --> 00:25:41,080
 Imate ono trenutke tišine,

685
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:43,780
 malo ona violina tamo svira

686
00:25:43,780 --> 00:25:46,740
 i onda kreće molitva svečanika

687
00:25:46,740 --> 00:25:49,040
 koja se na jezicima tamo ponavlja,

688
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,480
 a prevodi

689
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:51,780
 i onda opet tišina.

690
00:25:51,780 --> 00:25:54,980
 I prije nego što svečanje krene govoriti,

691
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:57,140
 meni dragi gospodin

692
00:25:57,140 --> 00:26:00,560
 govori u srcu

693
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:03,980
 sve što mi je rekao u srcu,

694
00:26:03,980 --> 00:26:05,260
 gospodin mi kaže

695
00:26:05,260 --> 00:26:09,140
 sad ćeš čuti od riječi do riječi

696
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:10,780
 i ću ti ponoviti preko svečanika.

697
00:26:10,780 --> 00:26:12,520
 Želim te utvrditi,

698
00:26:12,520 --> 00:26:16,800
 uspoznaj da si ludo ljubljen

699
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:19,320
 i želim da slušaš moj glas.

700
00:26:19,320 --> 00:26:21,540
 To je poanta za tvoj život,

701
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:25,020
 slušat i uživat u mome glasu.

702
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:26,940
 A on će ti sve objašnjavati.

703
00:26:26,940 --> 00:26:29,860
 I krene svečanje govoriti,

704
00:26:29,860 --> 00:26:32,260
 gledajte, ja sad za ovo nemam svjedoka,

705
00:26:32,260 --> 00:26:33,820
 tu sam bio ja i gospodin.

706
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:37,200
 Ali od riječi do riječi.

707
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,200
 Ne da ja sam to...

708
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,820
 Znate, kad mi molimo za ljude

709
00:26:41,820 --> 00:26:45,320
 i kad dođu ljudi na osobnu molitvu,

710
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:49,500
 imaju potrebu da mi moliteli njima

711
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:51,060
 kažemo ono što oni hoće čuti.

712
00:26:51,060 --> 00:26:52,360
 Ti sad dobiješ neku riječ,

713
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:55,780
 kažeš im i oni to pa tomaće na svoj način.

714
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:56,700
 I on ti dođe i kaže,

715
00:26:56,700 --> 00:26:59,040
 pa ono što je došlo preko tebe u molitvi,

716
00:26:59,260 --> 00:27:01,500
 pa nije ti tako rečeno čovječ,

717
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,520
 osjećam se ono.

718
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:04,960
 Ti tak si htio čuti ili htjela čuti.

719
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:06,840
 Znači ovdje nije bilo tako.

720
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:08,820
 Ja sam čuo riječi do riječi.

721
00:27:08,820 --> 00:27:11,140
 Cijelo klanjanje, sljedeće klanjanje,

722
00:27:11,140 --> 00:27:12,300
 opet ista stvar.

723
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:15,280
 Možete zamisliti koje je to u meni

724
00:27:15,280 --> 00:27:16,540
 prouzrakovalo radost.

725
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:20,660
 Ne spektakel, ne ono wow, ne.

726
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:22,420
 Jer to ne možeš nikom objasniti.

727
00:27:22,420 --> 00:27:25,840
 Ja čak dva, tri puta sam možda svjedočio.

728
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:28,000
 Jer mi je to bilo glupo svjedočiti.

729
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:29,300
 To je nekako intima, ono.

730
00:27:29,300 --> 00:27:31,780
 Ali ovdje nekako sam osjećao

731
00:27:31,780 --> 00:27:33,480
 da baš tu stvar treba reći.

732
00:27:33,480 --> 00:27:38,200
 To je delirij u duši moje nastalo.

733
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,800
 Jer sam čuo tatu.

734
00:27:39,800 --> 00:27:41,740
 To je to.

735
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:44,560
 Za mene od toga danas se život promijenio.

736
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:46,020
 Ja sam se vratio u osjek

737
00:27:46,020 --> 00:27:48,800
 oslobođen od svih smrtnih grijeha.

738
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:51,620
 Kad sam imao životnu ispovijed,

739
00:27:51,620 --> 00:27:53,500
 ušao u sakramentalno život, naravno.

740
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:56,720
 Ali od tog trenutka, od te spoznaje

741
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,940
 da sam ljubljen,

742
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:59,620
 sve su meni promijenilo.

743
00:27:59,620 --> 00:28:01,440
 Cijeli moj život.

744
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,340
 I to je bio trenutak,

745
00:28:03,340 --> 00:28:05,600
 koji je centralni trenutak u mome životu.

746
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:06,800
 Moja žena Dajana,

747
00:28:06,800 --> 00:28:08,240
 koju ludo volim,

748
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,180
 i moja djeca,

749
00:28:09,180 --> 00:28:10,640
 su samo bonus.

750
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,900
 to je samo bonus.

751
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:16,160
 To oni su moje čuđenje.

752
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:20,320
 Je moguće da me toliko voliš, Isuse.

753
00:28:20,320 --> 00:28:25,420
 Da ti nije dovoljno da me u srcu to progovoraš,

754
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:27,960
 nego imaš potrebu da mi daš suprugu,

755
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,920
 djecu, da mi daš zajednicu moju.

756
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:32,460
 Pa ti imaš potrebu,

757
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:35,460
 meni ne prestano pokazati da si lud za mnom.

758
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,740
 To je ljubavni odnos.

759
00:28:37,740 --> 00:28:38,920
 To je ludilo.

760
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:42,600
 To mene vodi cijeli moj život

761
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:44,120
 od kad sam susreo gospodina.

762
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:45,560
 Hvala Bogu,

763
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:46,640
 to se ne mijenja.

764
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:48,040
 To se ne mijenja.

765
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,080
 I kada padnem,

766
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,820
 i kada sam slab,

767
00:28:50,820 --> 00:28:52,800
 i kada me grijeh uhvati iz grabi,

768
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:54,620
 brzo se vratim.

769
00:28:54,620 --> 00:28:56,280
 Gospodin me vrati ovo istinu.

770
00:28:56,440 --> 00:28:59,520
 Jer to je iskustvo koje obilježen sam.

771
00:28:59,520 --> 00:29:01,720
 Obilježen sam.

772
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:04,060
 A znam da ste i vi.

773
00:29:04,060 --> 00:29:06,760
 I baš sam sretan da možemo to zajedno djeliti.

774
00:29:06,760 --> 00:29:12,140
 Još jedan događaj zanimljiv u Međugorje je.

775
00:29:12,140 --> 00:29:13,940
 U tom sam zanosu.

776
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:16,840
 Sa drugi put sam došao sa jednom ekipom

777
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:18,560
 i došao sam sa jednim dečkom

778
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:20,340
 koji je bio pun darova duha svetog.

779
00:29:20,340 --> 00:29:21,280
 On je sad pokojni.

780
00:29:21,280 --> 00:29:22,520
 On je mene,

781
00:29:22,520 --> 00:29:26,260
 on mi je pomogao da uđem u ove karizmatske stvarnosti.

782
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,460
 Moj brat Jonatan.

783
00:29:27,460 --> 00:29:30,020
 Divan, divan brat.

784
00:29:30,020 --> 00:29:32,540
 Mi došli u Međugorje.

785
00:29:32,540 --> 00:29:34,420
 Idemo mi na klanjanje na misu.

786
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:37,140
 On kaže, ja ću iti spavat, umoran sam.

787
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:38,760
 Ne mogu, niš, ne funkcioniram.

788
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:40,260
 Mi psa, mi po dješta ti,

789
00:29:40,260 --> 00:29:41,520
 ti ćeš klanjanje propustiti.

790
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,500
 Ne, umoran sam.

791
00:29:42,500 --> 00:29:43,400
 Baš je bio na Jona.

792
00:29:43,400 --> 00:29:44,680
 Ima jednu prgavost onako.

793
00:29:44,680 --> 00:29:45,980
 Umoran sam.

794
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:47,120
 Pustite me na miru, kaže.

795
00:29:47,120 --> 00:29:49,180
 Dobro, koji ide spavati,

796
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:49,860
 to je Jona.

797
00:29:49,860 --> 00:29:51,860
 Svi ono, koji ga znali, to je Jona.

798
00:29:51,860 --> 00:29:53,180
 Ošao on spavati.

799
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:56,140
 Ja u crkvi, nas nekoliko u crkvi.

800
00:29:56,140 --> 00:29:59,500
 Nemam ženu, Dajanu sam sam.

801
00:29:59,500 --> 00:30:03,160
 Razmišljam da ću, možda ću biti apostol neki novi.

802
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,740
 Tako, ono, tam sam zanosu.

803
00:30:04,740 --> 00:30:06,800
 Imam prsten oče našona.

804
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,720
 To se tad prije furalo.

805
00:30:11,200 --> 00:30:16,220
 Ja u crkvi i kak je ono, klanjanje unutra sad,

806
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:19,460
 vadim taj prsten.

807
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:21,400
 U duhu gledam gospodina.

808
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:24,220
 Vjerujem da u duhu, u mašti kako hoćete,

809
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:26,360
 vjerujem da je to sad on što vidim.

810
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:29,380
 I imam potrebu, skinem taj prsten.

811
00:30:29,380 --> 00:30:32,440
 Izgovaram riječi koje su nepoznate za mene,

812
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:34,400
 jer nisam ništa čitao na tu temu

813
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,700
 ili bio, općenito nisam na početku

814
00:30:36,700 --> 00:30:38,880
 bio nešto od znanja i čitanja,

815
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,840
 nego ono, samo ljubav

816
00:30:40,840 --> 00:30:42,300
 koju osjećam u sebi.

817
00:30:42,300 --> 00:30:44,380
 I ja staljam te prsten

818
00:30:44,380 --> 00:30:45,960
 i kažem, gospodine,

819
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:48,120
 primi ovaj prsten

820
00:30:48,120 --> 00:30:51,140
 kao znak mojih zaruka za tebe.

821
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:52,300
 I ono,

822
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:54,340
 jer se mogu mušklaci zaručiti

823
00:30:54,340 --> 00:30:55,680
 pitanje koje se ona postavlja,

824
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:59,300
 ali osjećam da to su te duhovne zaruke.

825
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:01,460
 Ja želim biti tvoj zaručnik.

826
00:31:01,460 --> 00:31:03,040
 Ja tebi pripadam.

827
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:04,200
 Ti si moja ljubav.

828
00:31:05,320 --> 00:31:06,460
 I čujem, gospodina

829
00:31:06,460 --> 00:31:08,920
 u tome svome doživljaju

830
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:12,020
 kako uzima taj prsten

831
00:31:12,020 --> 00:31:13,400
 i prihvaća te zaruke.

832
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:16,580
 Kaže da od današi smo ti i ja zaručeni.

833
00:31:16,580 --> 00:31:17,920
 Gledajte.

834
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:24,480
 Da to nije bio Isus,

835
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,960
 ja vam nemam problem s tim.

836
00:31:25,960 --> 00:31:29,740
 Da to sve nije bio, gospodin.

837
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:31,340
 Nemam problem s tim.

838
00:31:31,340 --> 00:31:33,240
 Možda neki moji doživljaju, ok.

839
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:36,120
 Ali to je meni cijeli život promijenilo.

840
00:31:36,120 --> 00:31:38,640
 I da nije bio Isus, da je moja mašta,

841
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:40,020
 Bože, hvala ti na mašti.

842
00:31:40,020 --> 00:31:42,280
 To je promijenilo moj život.

843
00:31:42,280 --> 00:31:44,120
 Dolazimo mi nekoliko,

844
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:45,620
 doživili smo slične iskustva,

845
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:47,500
 nas nekoliko taj dan u crkvi.

846
00:31:48,000 --> 00:31:50,180
 Ja se vraćam u pansijon.

847
00:31:50,180 --> 00:31:51,880
 Ono, imam mojšta,

848
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,800
 da mi je kosa sjeda ko moj siju,

849
00:31:53,800 --> 00:31:55,400
 da sam doživio svjetlost.

850
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:59,640
 Vraćam se i ulječem u sobu kod moga Ione.

851
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,480
 Marko, moram ga probojiti,

852
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:02,800
 ja moram ovo podijeliti s nekim.

853
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:04,900
 Ja ušao unutra,

854
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:06,820
 I ona ima onako dugu kosu,

855
00:32:06,820 --> 00:32:08,160
 razbacala mu se kosa,

856
00:32:08,160 --> 00:32:09,380
 vidim da on bleji.

857
00:32:09,380 --> 00:32:10,640
 Ja kažem,

858
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:13,240
 I ona, znaš šta sam doživio čovječe?

859
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:13,780
 Ej.

860
00:32:13,780 --> 00:32:16,200
 Kaže, on, čekaj, čekaj, čekaj,

861
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,540
 znaš šta sam ja doživio?

862
00:32:18,140 --> 00:32:19,600
 Ma, pusti, ti si spavo,

863
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:21,500
 šta god da si ti doživio,

864
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:23,860
 ja sam, e, moram ti ovo reći.

865
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,400
 I kao, ajde, ajde, kao ti prvi.

866
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,900
 Ja mu kažem,

867
00:32:26,900 --> 00:32:28,380
 da sam se zaručio za Isusa.

868
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:31,020
 A on se hvata za glavu,

869
00:32:31,020 --> 00:32:31,720
 plače,

870
00:32:31,720 --> 00:32:33,740
 ja ne mogu vjerovat, kaže.

871
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,600
 Vidi ovo, uzima bilježnic,

872
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:36,820
 svak mi daje, ajde, čitaj.

873
00:32:36,820 --> 00:32:39,020
 Kaže, on je išao,

874
00:32:39,020 --> 00:32:40,420
 kad je išao to spavati,

875
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:43,020
 dobio je potica od gospodina,

876
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:45,960
 ajde uđi u molitvu,

877
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:48,340
 kad već nisi išao na klanjanje,

878
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:49,540
 klekni, moli,

879
00:32:49,540 --> 00:32:51,360
 uzmi papir i olovku, piši.

880
00:32:51,360 --> 00:32:54,540
 Imam nadahnute riječi za tebe,

881
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:55,140
 za Ivana,

882
00:32:55,140 --> 00:32:56,360
 za još nekoliko ljudi.

883
00:32:56,360 --> 00:32:59,960
 I, ja sam čital odmah za sebe

884
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:02,600
 i piše, kaže,

885
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:05,420
 on ima doživljaj da čuje

886
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:08,160
 gospine, gospine riječi za nas.

887
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,420
 I slušajte ovo.

888
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,560
 Kaže,

889
00:33:10,560 --> 00:33:14,080
 piše onda mu da je gospodina rekao za mene.

890
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,540
 Ivane,

891
00:33:15,540 --> 00:33:17,820
 ljubljen i zaručniče

892
00:33:17,820 --> 00:33:18,660
 mojega sina.

893
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:21,260
 Čovječe.

894
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:23,320
 Pa, rekao, to je to.

895
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:24,240
 To je to.

896
00:33:24,240 --> 00:33:26,220
 Kreće neki apostolat ludi,

897
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:27,580
 sve ostavljamo,

898
00:33:27,580 --> 00:33:29,660
 idemo uz dvije haljine po svijetu.

899
00:33:29,660 --> 00:33:31,960
 Taj trenutak,

900
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:32,500
 jedna cijela,

901
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:34,120
 bili su te sad riječi,

902
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:35,440
 koje su moje,

903
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:37,360
 nebitne za van,

904
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:39,340
 ali ovaj trenutak,

905
00:33:39,340 --> 00:33:40,080
 pazite vi to,

906
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:43,980
 vidjet ćete zašto je to kasnije bitno za moj život,

907
00:33:43,980 --> 00:33:46,200
 ali zapravo zašto je to bitno za sve nas.

908
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,520
 Jer moje svjedočanstvo,

909
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:49,480
 kao i sva svjedočanstva,

910
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:50,560
 koje ste i ovdje čuli,

911
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,580
 koje ćete čuti,

912
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:53,340
 su svjedočanstva,

913
00:33:53,340 --> 00:33:55,620
 kroz koje Bog želi reći svima,

914
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:56,860
 vidiš,

915
00:33:56,860 --> 00:33:58,160
 u toj situaciji,

916
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:58,980
 ja sam Bog,

917
00:33:58,980 --> 00:33:59,720
 živ sam,

918
00:33:59,720 --> 00:34:00,920
 s tobom sam.

919
00:34:00,920 --> 00:34:02,520
 u toj situaciji,

920
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:03,500
 u tom svjedočanstvu,

921
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:04,960
 sva su svjedočanstva drugačija,

922
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,600
 različita

923
00:34:05,600 --> 00:34:07,140
 i tu je Bog hoće,

924
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,980
 kroz svjedoke reći,

925
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:10,200
 ej, ovo govorim tebi.

926
00:34:10,200 --> 00:34:11,980
 Svjedok je bitan,

927
00:34:11,980 --> 00:34:13,440
 jer sam lud za njim,

928
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:15,540
 ali ne zaustajam si ja na njemu.

929
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:17,260
 Ti si jednako bitan,

930
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:19,460
 zato sam njega stavio da tebi to kažem.

931
00:34:19,460 --> 00:34:20,540
 Tu je ključ,

932
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,420
 a vidjet ćete kako to ima sve smisla.

933
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:25,180
 I nakon toga,

934
00:34:25,180 --> 00:34:26,180
 evo, nova potvrda,

935
00:34:26,180 --> 00:34:27,820
 Bog je uz mene,

936
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:29,660
 vraćam se,

937
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:31,840
 vraćam se u osjek

938
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:34,620
 i donosim to svjedočanstvo

939
00:34:34,620 --> 00:34:35,400
 drugim ljudima.

940
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:36,540
 Ljudi mi prilaze,

941
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:38,180
 kažu, čoveče,

942
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,380
 toto on si se promijenio,

943
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:40,220
 ono, znamo te,

944
00:34:40,220 --> 00:34:41,840
 miran si.

945
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:42,920
 Svi su mi govorili

946
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:45,140
 da neki je čudesan mir na meni.

947
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:46,200
 To je jako bilo zanimljivo,

948
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:48,300
 dok ja onako nisam to tako osjećao,

949
00:34:48,300 --> 00:34:50,180
 ali to bi svako rekao,

950
00:34:50,180 --> 00:34:52,640
 neki poseban mir iz tebe izlazi.

951
00:34:52,640 --> 00:34:54,180
 I ništa,

952
00:34:54,180 --> 00:34:56,640
 ja tu lagano ljudima donosim svjedočanstvo,

953
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:59,760
 shlačam kroz ovaj nutarni glas

954
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:02,880
 da gospodi mi daje milost,

955
00:35:02,880 --> 00:35:04,940
 da mu se stavim na raspolaganje

956
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:05,760
 za druge ljude,

957
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:07,860
 dobijam nadahnute riječi,

958
00:35:07,860 --> 00:35:09,820
 počnem pričati iz ničega,

959
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:11,120
 bez ikakve pripreme,

960
00:35:11,120 --> 00:35:12,540
 ljudi počinju plakati,

961
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:14,180
 pa to se odnosi na mene,

962
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:15,600
 to dira moje srce,

963
00:35:15,600 --> 00:35:16,940
 to je moja situacija,

964
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:18,400
 kao da mi srce gledaš.

965
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:20,600
 Pa počinjem moliti za ljude

966
00:35:20,600 --> 00:35:22,400
 i stvari se počinju događati

967
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:25,920
 i u jednom trenutku,

968
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:28,960
 nakon sad prošle ne znam neka godina,

969
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,700
 ja molim za ljude,

970
00:35:30,700 --> 00:35:32,400
 vraćam se u svoju kuću,

971
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:34,120
 kod pokojne bake sam

972
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:36,860
 i ulazim u jedan razgovor sa gospodinom.

973
00:35:38,040 --> 00:35:39,560
 Prvo mu govorim jednu stvar.

974
00:35:39,560 --> 00:35:40,900
 Prvo kažem, gospodine,

975
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:42,840
 ovo sa što se događa,

976
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:45,520
 svaki dan je nešto bila intenzivno,

977
00:35:45,520 --> 00:35:46,300
 nemam nikoga,

978
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:48,000
 mlad sam,

979
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,240
 samo moliš,

980
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:50,280
 ideš, svjedočiš.

981
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:52,460
 Ja kažem, gospodine,

982
00:35:52,460 --> 00:35:54,340
 ovo neće biti dobro

983
00:35:54,340 --> 00:35:56,360
 ako ja ne dobijem svečenika.

984
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,420
 Imam potrebu za svečenikom.

985
00:35:58,420 --> 00:36:00,840
 Imam potrebu da imam duhovnika,

986
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,720
 da me neko vodi.

987
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:04,240
 Ja ne želim i bojim se ovojiti sam.

988
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:06,860
 I čujem u svome srcu

989
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:09,240
 daću ti svečenika,

990
