 Samo do neke mjere.

2279
01:13:40,900 --> 01:13:43,400
 I oni mi otkazuju nekoliko proizvoda

2280
01:13:43,400 --> 01:13:44,740
 koje godinama uzimaju,

2281
01:13:44,740 --> 01:13:47,080
 na kojima mi malte ne i živimo.

2282
01:13:47,080 --> 01:13:48,440
 Šta ću sad?

2283
01:13:48,440 --> 01:13:51,240
 Ja kažem, Bože moj, šta se događa?

2284
01:13:51,240 --> 01:13:52,520
 Samo mi vjeruj.

2285
01:13:52,520 --> 01:13:54,940
 Prvi mjesec, drugi, treći,

2286
01:13:54,940 --> 01:13:55,720
 na nuli sam,

2287
01:13:55,720 --> 01:13:57,600
 neki blagi minus,

2288
01:13:57,600 --> 01:13:59,860
 a kredit sam digao,

2289
01:13:59,860 --> 01:14:02,140
 4100 kuna svaki mjesec,

2290
01:14:02,140 --> 01:14:05,360
 sam sam, nemam nikog zaposlenog kušnja,

2291
01:14:05,360 --> 01:14:06,440
 a gospodin kaže,

2292
01:14:06,440 --> 01:14:08,460
 tebe tražim vjeru do kraja.

2293
01:14:08,460 --> 01:14:10,240
 To je jako bitno za tvoj život.

2294
01:14:10,900 --> 01:14:11,920
 I ja kažem, gospodine,

2295
01:14:11,920 --> 01:14:13,940
 molim te, pomozi mi samo ovaj put.

2296
01:14:13,940 --> 01:14:15,640
 Travam mi pomoć.

2297
01:14:15,640 --> 01:14:17,100
 Poprosti što sumnjam.

2298
01:14:17,100 --> 01:14:18,360
 Travam mi pomoć.

2299
01:14:18,360 --> 01:14:20,920
 Vjerujem, ali borim se ako pomozi mi.

2300
01:14:20,920 --> 01:14:22,620
 I gospodin kaže, malovjerni,

2301
01:14:22,620 --> 01:14:24,100
 malovjerni,

2302
01:14:24,100 --> 01:14:26,360
 sad ću ti pomoć

2303
01:14:26,360 --> 01:14:29,800
 i više me po tom pitanju ne traži.

2304
01:14:29,800 --> 01:14:32,480
 Moraš živjeti od moje riječi

2305
01:14:32,480 --> 01:14:34,760
 i od onog što ti stavljam u srce.

2306
01:14:34,760 --> 01:14:37,480
 A sve inače što mi gospodin stavlja u srce,

2307
01:14:37,480 --> 01:14:38,940
 stavljam pred svog duhovnika.

2308
01:14:39,420 --> 01:14:41,580
 Sad ja imam duhovnika već drugi niz godina,

2309
01:14:41,580 --> 01:14:42,980
 naš patr je Sebastijan

2310
01:14:42,980 --> 01:14:45,200
 i ništa ne radim bez duhovnika.

2311
01:14:45,200 --> 01:14:46,180
 Da se razumemo.

2312
01:14:46,180 --> 01:14:50,060
 Kaže mi, gospodin,

2313
01:14:50,060 --> 01:14:51,840
 doći će ti jedan čovjek,

2314
01:14:51,840 --> 01:14:53,520
 uzeti će ti robe,

2315
01:14:53,520 --> 01:14:54,780
 kaže mi njegovu ime,

2316
01:14:54,780 --> 01:14:56,300
 za 30.000 kuna.

2317
01:14:56,300 --> 01:14:58,080
 To će ti biti znak

2318
01:14:58,080 --> 01:15:00,960
 i više ne smiješ da od meni traži pomoć po tom pitanju.

2319
01:15:01,800 --> 01:15:03,520
 Jer to je naša firma, ne tvoja.

2320
01:15:03,520 --> 01:15:04,960
 Ja zove moju ženu,

2321
01:15:04,960 --> 01:15:05,820
 ona je svjedok.

2322
01:15:05,820 --> 01:15:08,100
 Čovječe u srcu sam dobio,

2323
01:15:08,100 --> 01:15:10,840
 doći će taj i taj uzeti robu za 300.000 kuna.

2324
01:15:10,840 --> 01:15:12,180
 Dan ili dva,

2325
01:15:12,180 --> 01:15:13,360
 to zaboravim,

2326
01:15:13,360 --> 01:15:13,900
 nebitno,

2327
01:15:13,900 --> 01:15:15,100
 dolazi taj čovjek.

2328
01:15:15,780 --> 01:15:17,040
 Nijesam nam radio do sada.

2329
01:15:17,040 --> 01:15:17,820
 Kaže,

2330
01:15:17,820 --> 01:15:19,520
 mali, čuo sam si ti kupio firmu.

2331
01:15:19,520 --> 01:15:20,440
 Ja kažem,

2332
01:15:20,440 --> 01:15:21,240
 pa da, jesam.

2333
01:15:21,240 --> 01:15:22,400
 Ajde, šta ti to imaš?

2334
01:15:22,400 --> 01:15:23,200
 Ajde, šta ti to?

2335
01:15:23,200 --> 01:15:24,720
 Pa kojene maliki keksi,

2336
01:15:24,720 --> 01:15:26,340
 ajde, daj mi paletu.

2337
01:15:26,340 --> 01:15:28,900
 Daj mi ovo tijesto.

2338
01:15:28,900 --> 01:15:29,460
 Daj mi ovo,

2339
01:15:29,460 --> 01:15:30,120
 daj mi ono.

2340
01:15:30,120 --> 01:15:31,240
 Možeš to donijet,

2341
01:15:31,240 --> 01:15:31,900
 kaže sutra.

2342
01:15:31,900 --> 01:15:32,500
 Danas.

2343
01:15:32,500 --> 01:15:33,780
 Mogu, rekao,

2344
01:15:33,780 --> 01:15:34,420
 nema problema.

2345
01:15:34,420 --> 01:15:35,600
 Ja pišem ko ono,

2346
01:15:35,600 --> 01:15:36,700
 mali miš skačem,

2347
01:15:36,700 --> 01:15:37,740
 čovječe,

2348
01:15:37,740 --> 01:15:38,800
 što se ovo događa.

2349
01:15:38,800 --> 01:15:40,480
 Nemam kombi,

2350
01:15:40,480 --> 01:15:41,040
 nemam ništa,

2351
01:15:41,140 --> 01:15:42,500
 obećavam sve,

2352
01:15:42,500 --> 01:15:43,580
 mone frke samo,

2353
01:15:43,580 --> 01:15:43,920
 rekao.

2354
01:15:43,920 --> 01:15:45,700
 Riješćem,

2355
01:15:45,700 --> 01:15:46,160
 dobez ću,

2356
01:15:46,160 --> 01:15:47,040
 ako treba na leđima.

2357
01:15:47,040 --> 01:15:49,420
 Kud sam ja račun,

2358
01:15:49,420 --> 01:15:51,700
 30 tisuća kuna.

2359
01:15:51,700 --> 01:15:54,880
 30 tisuća kuna.

2360
01:15:54,880 --> 01:15:55,560
 Plačem,

2361
01:15:55,560 --> 01:15:57,420
 kajem se za sumnju,

2362
01:15:57,420 --> 01:15:58,400
 kajem se,

2363
01:15:58,400 --> 01:15:59,360
 sajste se kajem,

2364
01:15:59,360 --> 01:16:01,260
 opet sumnjaš

2365
01:16:01,260 --> 01:16:03,300
 i zahvaljujem gospodinu,

2366
01:16:03,300 --> 01:16:04,620
 predaj mu financije,

2367
01:16:04,620 --> 01:16:05,580
 financijski dio.

2368
01:16:05,580 --> 01:16:07,060
 Dolazi jedno dijete,

2369
01:16:07,060 --> 01:16:07,920
 drugo treće,

2370
01:16:07,920 --> 01:16:10,120
 za svaki blagoslov,

2371
01:16:10,320 --> 01:16:11,580
 sa svako dijete blagoslov.

2372
01:16:11,580 --> 01:16:13,060
 Ulazimo,

2373
01:16:13,060 --> 01:16:13,540
 kupujemo,

2374
01:16:13,540 --> 01:16:14,660
 jedan stan,

2375
01:16:14,660 --> 01:16:15,220
 mali,

2376
01:16:15,220 --> 01:16:16,080
 iz iznanjljenoga,

2377
01:16:16,080 --> 01:16:17,960
 50 kvadrata,

2378
01:16:17,960 --> 01:16:19,520
 dolazi treće dijete,

2379
01:16:19,520 --> 01:16:21,740
 kuća 150 kvadrata,

2380
01:16:21,740 --> 01:16:25,160
 u cijeni koja je nerealna

2381
01:16:25,160 --> 01:16:26,020
 u ovom ludilu,

2382
01:16:26,020 --> 01:16:26,400
 sad,

2383
01:16:26,400 --> 01:16:27,320
 sadašnjem,

2384
01:16:27,320 --> 01:16:29,320
 prošle godine smo kupili kuću,

2385
01:16:29,320 --> 01:16:31,300
 nevjerojatni božji zahvat

2386
01:16:31,300 --> 01:16:32,260
 i gospodin kaže,

2387
01:16:32,260 --> 01:16:33,160
 tu sam,

2388
01:16:33,160 --> 01:16:34,620
 tu sam,

2389
01:16:34,620 --> 01:16:35,540
 ne boj se.

2390
01:16:35,540 --> 01:16:38,840
 Za vas koji ste u zajednici,

2391
01:16:39,500 --> 01:16:42,080
 obitelj nije svrha samoj sebi.

2392
01:16:42,080 --> 01:16:44,860
 Ovo što mi je gospodin dao

2393
01:16:44,860 --> 01:16:46,400
 i što ja sad dajem vama,

2394
01:16:46,400 --> 01:16:49,860
 to nije svrha samoj sebi.

2395
01:16:50,460 --> 01:16:53,880
 To je samo znak da je Bog uz nas.

2396
01:16:53,880 --> 01:16:58,780
 I Bog želi da gradimo crkvu kućnu,

2397
01:16:58,780 --> 01:17:00,660
 da se obnovi seopća crkva.

2398
01:17:00,660 --> 01:17:03,220
 Staleške dužnosti su ključne.

2399
01:17:03,220 --> 01:17:05,980
 U njima je žrvanj moje i naše svetosti.

2400
01:17:05,980 --> 01:17:10,000
 I žrvnja te svetosti i žrvnja te bitke,

2401
01:17:10,000 --> 01:17:11,920
 mi idemo u evangelizaciju.

2402
01:17:11,920 --> 01:17:15,680
 I Bog želi dvije stvari od mene,

2403
01:17:15,680 --> 01:17:18,300
 a ja ću reći možda želji od vas.

2404
01:17:18,300 --> 01:17:20,560
 Želi da sam prvo u obitelji

2405
01:17:20,560 --> 01:17:22,560
 i da ljubavlju,

2406
01:17:22,560 --> 01:17:26,300
 riječima, dijelima pokazujem ljubav

2407
01:17:26,300 --> 01:17:27,980
 i da tako vodim obitelj.

2408
01:17:27,980 --> 01:17:32,280
 Ali onda želi i da primjerom pokaže

2409
01:17:32,280 --> 01:17:35,000
 mojoj djeci šta je tati najbitnije.

2410
01:17:35,000 --> 01:17:37,600
 Iz te sređenosti i žrtve,

2411
01:17:37,600 --> 01:17:38,680
 nije uvijek sve super,

2412
01:17:38,680 --> 01:17:41,280
 idem u zajednicu

2413
01:17:41,280 --> 01:17:43,560
 i moja me djeca vidjet gdje služim.

2414
01:17:43,560 --> 01:17:46,040
 Znači nema zaustavljanja

2415
01:17:46,040 --> 01:17:48,300
 dok se ne sredimo financijski

2416
01:17:48,300 --> 01:17:49,920
 ili Bog sad hoće da sam samo

2417
01:17:49,920 --> 01:17:50,940
 od svoje obitelji, ne.

2418
01:17:50,940 --> 01:17:54,100
 Djeca žive od naše vjere,

2419
01:17:54,100 --> 01:17:55,620
 njihova vjera rastane

2420
01:17:55,620 --> 01:17:57,060
 gledaju tata je doma,

2421
01:17:57,060 --> 01:17:58,500
 na koljenima zeza se,

2422
01:17:58,500 --> 01:17:59,260
 glupira se,

2423
01:17:59,260 --> 01:18:00,480
 igdamo se autićima,

2424
01:18:00,480 --> 01:18:02,000
 ljubimo se,

2425
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:02,940
 tata sprema,

2426
01:18:02,940 --> 01:18:05,640
 tata radi sve da mami pomogne,

2427
01:18:05,640 --> 01:18:07,900
 da tako pokazuje mamu da voli,

2428
01:18:07,900 --> 01:18:09,640
 ali isto tako tata kaže

2429
01:18:09,640 --> 01:18:11,180
 idemo na zajednicu,

2430
01:18:11,180 --> 01:18:12,860
 idemo slaviti Boga,

2431
01:18:12,860 --> 01:18:14,600
 idemo moliti za drugu djecu,

2432
01:18:14,600 --> 01:18:16,040
 idemo donositi ljubav

2433
01:18:16,040 --> 01:18:17,100
 drugim obiteljima,

2434
01:18:17,100 --> 01:18:18,940
 gdje tata nije dobar,

2435
01:18:18,940 --> 01:18:20,280
 gdje tata nije u miru,

2436
01:18:20,280 --> 01:18:22,020
 gdje mama ne razumije stvari.

2437
01:18:22,020 --> 01:18:23,240
 Idemo zajedni,

2438
01:18:23,240 --> 01:18:24,940
 onda mi idemo kao obitelj

2439
01:18:24,940 --> 01:18:28,160
 i tada se događa evangelizacija.

2440
01:18:28,160 --> 01:18:30,620
 Mi smo primili hrpu milosti

2441
01:18:30,620 --> 01:18:32,820
 i zaustavali smo se na tome.

2442
01:18:32,820 --> 01:18:33,940
 Pogledajte sve spoznaje

2443
01:18:33,940 --> 01:18:35,480
 koje ste bi dobili ovdje

2444
01:18:35,480 --> 01:18:36,340
 na novorođenima.

2445
01:18:36,340 --> 01:18:38,440
 Šta radimo s tim spoznajama?

2446
01:18:38,440 --> 01:18:40,940
 Šta su one nama napravile?

2447
01:18:40,940 --> 01:18:41,980
 Koliko su vam pomogle?

2448
01:18:41,980 --> 01:18:44,820
 Koliko su vas bacile u taj deliri?

2449
01:18:45,380 --> 01:18:46,420
 Gospodin je živ.

2450
01:18:46,420 --> 01:18:48,680
 Da, jesam u svojoj obitelji,

2451
01:18:48,680 --> 01:18:49,880
 ali čovječe,

2452
01:18:49,880 --> 01:18:51,880
 pak se ja brinem za svoju obitelj,

2453
01:18:51,880 --> 01:18:53,120
 to je zbog se za nju brine.

2454
01:18:53,120 --> 01:18:56,720
 Pa onda Bog hoće da idem opušteno u drugu obitelj,

2455
01:18:56,720 --> 01:18:58,960
 ali tu moramo doći do slobode.

2456
01:19:00,600 --> 01:19:01,120
 Završavam.

2457
01:19:01,120 --> 01:19:02,340
 Evo, imao sam još,

2458
01:19:02,340 --> 01:19:03,860
 ali baš sam pretjerao,

2459
01:19:03,860 --> 01:19:04,640
 ispričavam se.

2460
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:07,500
 Ima sam još,

2461
01:19:07,500 --> 01:19:09,700
 htio sam vam pričati o iskustvu nemoći,

2462
01:19:09,700 --> 01:19:13,820
 kako svaki čovjek treba ući u to iskustvo nemoći,

2463
01:19:13,820 --> 01:19:16,080
 iz koje čovjek ulazi u slobodu,

2464
01:19:16,080 --> 01:19:19,200
 iz koje se javlja radost

2465
01:19:19,200 --> 01:19:20,620
 i prepuštanje Bogu,

2466
01:19:20,620 --> 01:19:22,020
 ali evo,

2467
01:19:22,020 --> 01:19:23,760
 to neki drugi put.

2468
01:19:23,760 --> 01:19:25,420
 Hvala vam lijepo.

